    "## 步骤 3：经典DID估计\n",
    "\n",
    "经典DID回归模型：\n",
    "\n",
    "$$Y_{it} = \alpha + \beta T_i + \gamma Post_t + \delta (T_i \times Post_t) + \epsilon_{it}$$\n",
    "\n",
    "其中 $\delta$ 就是DID估计量（ATT）。"
   ]
